					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5381838#post-3725248</guid>
				<title>Special Thanks</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5381838/scp-3421#post-3725248</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 01 Mar 2018 03:29:52 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>glewmie</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3448977</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Oh&nbsp;no!</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>The trees are only capable of using voice clips to communicate! If you notice, during the anomalous calls, (where Leigh isn't the one that's talking), the only words present are ones that have been used in previous conversations!</p> <p>Ideally, I can get some voice actresses to voice the parts in some actual audio logs, do some fancy effects and seal this SCP up!</p> </div> </div> </div> <p><strong>Special Thanks to:</strong></p> <ul> <li>Offline friends for providing ideas, support, and media for the project.</li> <li>Ratsy for taking the time to workshop some things with it.</li> <li>TheGreatHippo for workshopping lots of lines!</li> <li>FloppyPhoenix for introducing the idea of a discovery log first.</li> <li>Photosynthetic for grammatical fixes and tone shifts.</li> </ul> <p><strong>Image Credit</strong><br /> Image for &quot;Cell Tower Trees&quot; is used under written license from from:<br /> Creator: Andrew Tien<br /> Original Source: Personal Commission</p> 
				 	]]>
